title: #158: Pindar and The Black Nobility with Ras Ben
description: Thank you for tuning in for a bonus episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode I welcome one of the coolest cats on the planet, Ras Ben, to talk Black Nobility and Lizard People.  I put this out on the Patreon and it got such a good response I decided it out on the regular feed.  Thank you so much for your love and support.
